About
Overlooking the runway of the Miami International Airport, enjoy a fantastic view of the planes taking off and landing at the 94th Aero Squadron Restaurant in Miami. There are headphones available for you to listen to the air traffic ground control and you can see cargo trains pass right in front of your window while you dine.

EVENTS AT 94TH AERO SQUADRON
The 94thAero Squadron location setting will inspire your group to create, collaborate and engage with each other. Our venue’s unique spaces can accommodate all of your corporate events including conferences, board meetings, seminars and private dining. We also provide complimentary WIFI and audio/visual equipment. Ensuring your event is executed flawlessly is tops on our agenda.

The skilled and accommodating, in-house special events staff at The 94Th Aero Squadron is known for putting on dazzling and expertly orchestrated events. As seasoned professionals, The 94th Aero Squadron can create the perfect backdrop for any occasion. With expansive connections to cater to your every need, our team can handle anything from production planning services, exclusive custom menu spreads, venue design and decor, beautiful floral arrangements, and even technical services like audio and visual equipment needs.
Whatever your event calls for, The 94th Aero Squadron will deliver.
*WEDDINGS                                            *BABY & BRIDAL SHOWERS
*BIRTHDAY PARTIES                              *RETIREMENT PARTIES
*QUINCES                                               *BAR / BAT MITZVAHS
*REHEARSAL DINNERS                        *AWARDS DINNERS
